/frontend -> npm create vite@latest .

/backend -> npm init -y

/backend -> npm i express mongoose dotenv jsonwebtoken bcryptjs cookie-parser cloudinary socket.io

/backend -> npm i nodemon -D

package.json -> "scripts": {"dev": "nodemon index.js"},

package.json -> "type": "module", 추가 후 const express = require("express"); -> import express from "express"; 형태로 사용가능

/backend/src -> controllers, lib, middleware, models, routes 폴더 생성

create mongodb with Docker
docker run -d -p 30001:27018 --name slack_clone -v /Users/root1/Desktop/docker_v/slack_clone:/data/db -e MONGODB_INITDB_ROOT_USERNAME=root -e MONGODB_INITDB_ROOT_PASSWORD=1234 mongo

